snippet.textDisplay: Have lost count of how many times I have heard this song by now! Something strange connects me with this song... the lyrics.. voices.. the bass distortion which blends like honey with shehnai @3:35.. the complete arrangement has floored me! I have been a fan of Sachin-Jigar since a long time and have been following their work closely and have admired their guts to experiment with different Rhythm patterns which we rarely find in bollywood these days but this is an ace work which we cant compare with conventional Hindi film music ! Everytime i hear this song i fall in love with this song again and find a new dimension to the track! Take a bow Sachin-Jigar. You have owned me with this  :)
snippet.textOriginal: Have lost count of how many times I have heard this song by now! Something strange connects me with this song... the lyrics.. voices.. the bass distortion which blends like honey with shehnai @3:35.. the complete arrangement has floored me!
